” over the roofs of the world, is the subject of Turner’s revelatory study.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAuthors and publishersxHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aAuthors and publisherszUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aCensorshipxHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aCensorshipzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitics and literaturexHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aPolitics and literaturezUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aPublishers and publishingxHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aPublishers and publishingzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Books & Reading.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016731340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300167313423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300167313/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles